        @Nonnull
RoutineConfiguration.Builder<? extends TYPE> withRoutine()
        Gets the routine configuration builder related to this builder instance.
        The configuration options not supported by the builder implementation might be ignored.

        Note that the builder will be initialized with the current configuration.

        Returns:
        the routine configuration builder.
